OL,3,CMan admits murdering his wife 'out of
OL,4,Cthe blue' after argument
OL,6,FA man has admitted to killing his wife
OL,7,F'out of the blue' after an argument at
OL,8,Ftheir home in Brean.
OL,10,FSimon Steeves, 71, appeared at Bristol
OL,11,FCrown Court on Wednesday 7 February,
OL,12,Fwhere he pleaded guilty to murdering
OL,13,Fhis wife, 59-year-old Denise Steeves,
OL,14,Fat their home in Diamond Meadow Lodge
OL,15,FPark on 25 October 2023.
OL,17,FThe court heard how the defendant had
OL,18,Fstabbed his wife, then called 999 and
OL,19,Ftold police he had murdered her.
