OL,6,FAvon and Somerset Police were the
OL,7,Ffirst emergency service on the scene
OL,8,Fand arrested Steeves.
OL,10,FAn officer provided Denise with CPR
OL,11,Funtil paramedics arrived but despite
OL,12,Ftheir best efforts, .
OL,14,FWhen Steeves was interviewed, he
OL,15,Fadmitted to killing his wife following
OL,16,Fan argument, but 'did not remember
OL,17,Fpicking up the knife'.
OL,19,FHe was charged with murder the day
OL,20,Fafter the incident.
