OL,6,FSenior Investigating Officer,
OL,7,FDetective Inspector said: "My sincere
OL,8,Fcondolences and thoughts remain with
OL,9,Fthe family and loved ones of Denise,
OL,10,Fwho have supported our investigation
OL,11,Fsince the incident in October last
OL,12,Fyear.
OL,14,F"Steeves fatally wounded his wife out
OL,15,Fof the blue following an argument in
OL,16,Ftheir Brean home. There had previously
OL,17,Fbeen no reports of violence between
OL,18,Fthe pair.
