OL,6,F"I would like to take this opportunity
OL,7,Fto thank everyone who has supported
OL,8,Fthis investigation, including
OL,9,Fwitnesses, first responders and the
OL,10,Fteam who have worked tirelessly on
OL,11,Fthis case.
OL,13,F"We hope this gives Denise's loved
OL,14,Fones some closure, knowing the man who
OL,15,Ftook Denise from them too soon will
OL,16,Fsoon be in jail."
OL,18,FSteeves will appear at Bristol Crown
OL,19,FCourt on Friday 1 March for sentencing.
